data.description: Sunny Marysville home is ready for new owners. This 1,732 square foot home has 3 bedroom & 2.5 bathrooms. The generous kitchen has granite counters, island & casual dining area and opens to the living room & sunroom (not included in sq ft). A gas fireplace & large windows highlight the living room. Formal dining room (now a home office) features vaulted ceilings & skylights. Upstairs you will find a spacious primary suite with attached bath & walk-in closet. Primary's windows show peek-a-boo views of Puget Sound. 2 extra bedrooms & full bath. Home features a sunroom, private deck & fenced yard too. Don't miss the garage's shop space, air compressor, pressure washer & 2nd washer/dryer set. Lovely Northpointe neighborhood awaits. Welcome Home
